'''Unity'''是2010年4月建设完成的[[日本|日本]]与[[美国|美国]]之间的跨[[太平洋|太平洋]][[海底電纜|海底電纜]]系统。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/tech/world/2008-02-26-google-broadband-cable_N.htm|title=Google will help build trans-Pacific fiber-optic cable|date=26 February 2008|publisher=USA Today|accessdate=1 January 2012}}</ref><ref name="washpost1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/26/AR2008022601055.html|title=Google part of group building cable to Japan|date=26 February 2008|publisher=The Washington Post|accessdate=1 January 2012|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605235506/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/26/AR2008022601055.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/2008/02/26/idINIndia-32155620080226|title=Google, SingTel, others to build submarine cable|date=26 February 2008|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=1 January 2012|archive-date=2013-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130626132342/http://in.reuters.com/article/2008/02/26/idINIndia-32155620080226}}</ref>

Unity电缆系统由多条“太比特”电缆线路组成，总长度10,000公里<ref>{{cite web|title=Telstra 为UNITY海缆升级100Gbps系统|url=http://www.c-fol.net/news/content/1/201311/20131127075323.html|website=光纤在线|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-date=2020-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224201512/http://www.c-fol.net/news/content/1/201311/20131127075323.html}}</ref>，容量高达7.68 {{tsl|en|Tbit}}/s。<ref name="unity">Grahame Lynch "[http://www.commsday.com/commsday/?p=186 Google plans new undersea "Unity" cable across Pacific] {{Wayback|url=http://www.commsday.com/commsday/?p=186 |date=20110317094003 }}."</ref>线缆施工由{{tsl|en|Bharti_Airtel|Bharti Airtel}}、Global Transit、[[Google|Google]]、[[KDDI|KDDI]]、{{tsl|en|Pacnet|Pacnet}}和[[新加坡电信|新加坡电信]]在2008年2月组成的联合体出资。<ref name="unity"/>Unity的安装费用约为3亿美元，在完成后将增加约20%跨太平洋电缆容量。<ref name="washpost1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/26/AR2008022601055.html|title=Google part of group building cable to Japan|date=26 February 2008|publisher=The Washington Post|accessdate=1 January 2012}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
[[File:CS_Tyco_Responder-27527.jpg|右]]
2008年2月，由Bharti Airtel、Global Transit、Google、KDDI公司、Pacnet和新加坡电信组成的联合体宣布，他们将按协议建造一条高带宽海底光纤电缆，连接美国与日本，建设成本约3亿美元。<ref name="washpost1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/26/AR2008022601055.html|title=Google part of group building cable to Japan|date=26 February 2008|publisher=The Washington Post|accessdate=1 January 2012}}</ref>

签字仪式2008年2月23日在东京举行<ref>{{cite web|title=Google等6公司修建跨太平洋光缆|url=http://net.zdnet.com.cn/network_security_zone/2008/0616/928920.shtml|website=赛迪网|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-date=2016-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916210246/http://net.zdnet.com.cn/network_security_zone/2008/0616/928920.shtml}}</ref>，承包Unity的[[日本電氣|NEC公司]]和{{tsl|en|Tyco_International|泰科电讯}}将负责建设和安装该系统。两公司在2008年6月开始建设此项目。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/147467/work_begins_on_googlebacked_unity_undersea_cable.html|title=Work Begins on Google-backed 'Unity' Undersea Cable|date=24 June 2008|publisher=PC World|accessdate=1 January 2012|archive-date=2008-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080705002958/http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/147467/work_begins_on_googlebacked_unity_undersea_cable.html}}</ref>2009年11月，电缆抵达日本。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/181258/googlebacked_unity_cable_lands_in_japan.html|title=Google-backed Unity Cable Lands in Japan|date=3 November 2009|publisher=PC World|accessdate=1 January 2012|archive-date=2010-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100906181332/http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/181258/googlebacked_unity_cable_lands_in_japan.html}}</ref>2010年4月，电缆测试完毕，可以开始提供服务。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://biz.thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2010/4/2/business/5982231&|title=Unity cable set for service|date=2 April 2010|publisher=The Star|accessdate=1 January 2012|archive-date=2012-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623164918/http://biz.thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2010%2F4%2F2%2Fbusiness%2F5982231&}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/business/companies/article364772.ece|title=Bharti launches $300 m Unity cable system|date=1 April 2010|publisher=The Hindu|accessdate=1 January 2012}}</ref>

== 规格 ==
Unity是一条总长度约10,000公里的跨太平洋电缆，坐落在[[东京|东京]]附近[[千葉縣|千葉縣]]海岸的{{tsl|en|Chikura, Chiba|千仓町}}和[[美国西海岸|美国西海岸]]的[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]及其他网络接入点之间。Unity在千仓也连通其他电缆系统。

新的五光纤对电缆系统具有五对光纤，每个光纤对能提供高达每秒960吉比特（Gbit/s）的容量。凭借高光纤对数，Unity可以以较低单元成本提供更高容量。<ref>{{cite web|title=谷歌等六公司投资3亿美元合建美日海底光缆|url=http://tech.163.com/08/0226/11/45KILBU6000915BE.html|website=网易科技|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-date=2016-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814034310/http://tech.163.com/08/0226/11/45KILBU6000915BE.html}}</ref>

Unity初步预计将增加跨太平洋电缆系统的20%容量，增加每秒7.68太比特（Tbit/s）跨太平洋带宽。

